<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von gelts
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, des sich Peter
                                <expan>Steinberg<ex>er</ex></expan> und Thomas
                                <expan>Visch<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>unterfang<ex>en</ex></expan> süllen <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>von des <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> von Saffoy gelt</add> zu
                        beczaln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Parsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<pb facs="#facs_546" id="272r"/>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        wol ver<expan>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Thomas
                            <expan>Visch<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> niht ist. So <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Steynberg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu eren für uns besandt und fleissig mit im
                        davon reden <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, der meynt
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> selb <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
